HEADWORD: Evert
<hw>E*vert"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. & p.
p.</pos> <conjf>Everted</conjf>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Everting</conjf>.]</vmorph> <ety>[L. <ets>evertere</ets>. See
